body:
## Context
E2E Test Quality Report identified missing network failure simulation tests, which are critical for ensuring application resilience.

## Current Gap
- Network failure simulation incomplete
- API timeout handling not fully tested
- Offline mode behavior untested
- No automated recovery testing

## Required Test Scenarios

### 1. Network Failure Handling
```typescript
test('should handle network failures gracefully', async ({ page, context }) => {
  // Block all API requests
  await context.route('**/api/**', route => route.abort());

  await page.goto('/products');

  // Verify error UI appears
  await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="network-error"]')).toBeVisible();
  await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="retry-button"]')).toBeVisible();

  // Restore network and retry
  await context.unroute('**/api/**');
  await page.click('[data-testid="retry-button"]');
  await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="products-grid"]')).toBeVisible();
});
```

### 2. API Timeout Simulation
```typescript
test('should handle API timeouts', async ({ page, context }) => {
  // Delay API responses
  await context.route('**/api/**', async route => {
    await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 30000));
    await route.continue();
  });

  // Verify timeout handling
  await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="timeout-error"]')).toBeVisible();
});
```

### 3. Offline Mode Testing
- Test service worker offline queue
- Verify offline indicators
- Test sync when coming back online
- Validate cached data display

### 4. Partial Network Failures
- Some endpoints fail, others succeed
- Intermittent failures
- Slow network conditions
- Connection drops mid-request

## Technical Implementation
- Use Playwright's network interception
- Test across all browsers
- Include mobile network conditions
- Add performance metrics

## Success Criteria
- All network scenarios handled gracefully
- No data loss during failures
- Clear user feedback
- Automatic recovery works

## Dependencies
- Requires service worker implementation (#169)
- Related to error handling improvements

## SuperClaude Tools
Use `/sc:build --test --seq` for test patterns
Enable `--pup` for Playwright expertise

Effort: 12h
